---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Industrial Safety System">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="relative h-[300px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <img 
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504917595217-d4dc5ebe6122?w=1600" 
        alt="Industrial Safety" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Industrial Safety System</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Advanced AI PPE Detection</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Our system uses state-of-the-art artificial intelligence for detecting and monitoring personal protective equipment (PPE). We continuously monitor compliance with safety protocols and immediately alert any deviations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img 
          src="https://easyflow.tech/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/PPE-Detection-1.png"
          alt="AI PPE Detection"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div>
        <img 
          src="https://viso.ai/wp-content/smush-webp/2021/09/manufacturing-computer-vision-768x512.jpg.webp"
          alt="Worker in Protective Equipment"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Safety First</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          The system automatically identifies the presence and proper wearing of all necessary protective equipment, including helmets, safety glasses, vests, gloves, and protective footwear. This enables preventive action and maintenance of the highest workplace safety standards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mt-8">
      <h2>Real-time Monitoring</h2>
      <p>
        Our system provides instant alerts when safety protocol violations are detected, enabling quick intervention and prevention of potential accidents. Integration with existing security systems further increases the efficiency and reliability of the entire protection system.
      </p>

      <div class="my-8">
        <h2>See It In Action</h2>
        <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jOARPYVntEU"
            title="Product Demo"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            class="w-full h-[400px]"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>